headline: Ameriprise Financial Earns Two J.D. Power Certifications for Outstanding Client and Advisor Service
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, December 04, 2024--Ameriprise Financial, Inc. (NYSE: AMP) has received two J.D. Power certifications for delivering exceptional customer phone service to its clients and financial advisors. For the first time, the firm earned the "Outstanding Customer Service Experience" certification for the high level of service provided to clients. And, for the sixth consecutive year, the firm received the "Outstanding Customer Service Experience" certification for service provided to its advisor
